00:20:32.250 --> 00:20:34.500
Hey, Lucci! Sürükle onu!  

00:20:34.500 --> 00:20:36.708
Saçından tut!  

00:20:40.833 --> 00:20:42.375
Emir bu.  

00:20:42.375 --> 00:20:44.917
